{"title":"Fast Vrata Timing For You","description":"

Observe a fast on Saturdays for getting rid of malefic effects of Neptune. This fast is undertaken for 19 or 51 Saturdays by wearing blue or black clothes.

Massage oil on body, donate oil and worship peepal. Recite shani mantra on rudraksha beads as much as possible.

"}

data.name: Favourable lord model
data.body:
{"title":"Favourable Lord For You","description":"

Worship Ketu and Lord Narsimh. Recite daily the following mantra of Narsimh \"Om Hreem Ugram Veeram Maha Vishnum Jwalant Sarvatomukham Nrasimh Bheeshanam Bhadra Mrityu Mrityum Namamyaham Hreem\". Recite for a minimum 108 times daily.

Listen Satyanarayen katha on full Moon days. This shall relieve you of diseases and problems. If this recitation is not possible for you then visit the picture or deity of Lord Narsimh daily.

"}

data.name: Favourable time model
data.body:
{"title":"Favourable Time For You","description":"

According to western view the Sun remains in the sign of Cancer from 21st June to 25th July while according to Indian astrology this period is from 16th July to 16th August.

During this period there is an increase in water elements. Therefore this period is good for people with radical number 7 for beginning any new or important work.

"}

data.name: General house report model
data.body: {"planet":"sun","house_report":"You probably possess a desire to raise goals to a higher level and to seek ideas which would be of benefit for the group. Or you may desire to place your own goals and desires above the wishes of the group. You have the ability to make friends, many who are influential and wield power. You enjoy your work with groups. You are responsible, liberal and broad-minded. You are a humanitarian who would rather be popular than powerful. You have organizing ability and probably take the leadership role in group activities or friendly get-togethers."}

data.name: General rashi report model
data.body: {"planet":"moon","rashi_report":"You very easily respond to the emotional environment in which you are placed. You soak up feelings like a sponge. Perhaps this is why you so easily become moody, irritable and inconstant in thought and feeling. Learning to control your own moods may be very difficult, yet necessary, for you. Your greatest need is to nurture and mother someone or ones. You often appear irrational to others because you can't always explain the reason or source of your feelings. Anyone who lives with you must accept your ups and downs and appreciate your need for times of withdrawal. You are also very sympathetic and understand the unspoken feelings and needs of others. You take slights very personally and though you may forgive a mistake by a friend or loved one, you never forget it. Security is very important to you and you look for it in your home and family life. Your senses and emotions are quite strong and it would be wise for you to listen to your intuitive side as you can be quite psychic. You are very tenacious and you do not give up or let go of things or people easily. Your mother is/was a strong influence for good or ill in your life. You are basically an introvert, but will do whatever it takes to protect and defend your family or loved ones. You tend to be a pack-rat because everything has an emotional memory behind it and you find security in all those memories. Nothing or no one is ever gone if they leave their memory behind. Thus, you can become quite possessive. You have the memory of an elephant, but you must learn to forgive and forget past hurts."}

data.body:
{"title":"What the Number Says About You","description":"

Your Radical Number is 7. The ruler of number 7 according to Indian astrology is Ketu, while by western view it is Neptune. You will have little bit some effects of these planets on you. You will have plenty of imaginative power.

Poetry, music and songs, to watch T.V. are some activities you adore. Your interests will comprise of fine arts, writings, and literature etc. You will not have much financial success and piling up of money will be daunting for you. Travel, tourism, having fun etc will enthrall you.

You will establish expertise in reading others mind and in attracting people. In religion, you will follow new schools of thought and will distrust old customs and traditions. You will prefer jobs or trade related to travel and communication with distant lands.

Opportunities involving travel will be sought out by you. By virtue of your extrasensory faculties you will be able to read other persons mind. You will also have wonderful dreams. You will benefit from foreign lands, ships, cars etc.

"}
